    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Domnus imperator <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110"
                            >Ludovicus</persName> divina ordinante providentia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus, anno imperii eorum XXXIV,
                        tertiodecimo kalendas novembris, indictione decima. <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >Monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monks #Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            >beatissimorum apostolorum et Christi confessoris Silvestri</orgName>
                        sito <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Nonantulam</placeName>
                        in <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/38">Motinense</placeName>, ubi
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1219">Liutefredus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> esse videtur, ego in Dei nomine <persName
                            key="#vassusOf #Alemannus" ref="#people/1265">Warti</persName>
                        <rs key="#vassusOf">vassus</rs> domni imperatoris, legibus vivens <rs
                            key="#Alemannus">Allamannorum</rs>, presens presentibus dixi: Quisquis
                        in sanctis ac venerabilibus locis ex suis aliquid contulerit rebus, iuxta
                        auctoris vocem centuplum accipiet, et vitam possidebit eternam, ideo ego
                        Warti vassus domni imperatoris, dono et offero a die presenti in antea hac
                        venerabilem locum idest <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa curtem
                            massariciam</rs> iuris mei, quam habeo in loco et in fundo <placeName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Wine #Cereals #Forests #Fruits/vegetables #Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >Madio</placeName>, territorio <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cities #City_territory"
                            ref="#places/59">Veroniense</placeName>, tam mea porcionem, quamque
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Teobaldus">Teovaldi</name></persName> germano
                        meo, ut dictum est, tam casas cum <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">horto</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs> et <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs> vel
                        omnia et in omnibus quicquid in predicto loco vel inibi circiter ea per
                        singula loca et casaliam ad ipsa casa pertinet … et intus <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitate</rs> Verona casa in loco dicto <placeName key="#Houses"
                            >Cortina</placeName> … a <persName><name ref="Isaac"
                            >Isachio</name></persName> germ.. possessam, et defensatam fuerint …
                        sanctum hac venerabilem locum in subsidium <rs key="#Monks">fratrum</rs> do
                        et offero per presente cartula, … <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Andrea">Andrea</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">tradidit</rs> scribere rogavi, in qua subter confirmavi, …
                        Actum in civitate <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Cities #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            ref="#places/275">Mantua</placeName>, in <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Residential #Palatium">palacio</rs>
                        ...</ab>
